data.description:
PRICE DROP!!!!  Charming 3-2-2 with open floor plan in desirable neighborhood and school district. Large master and secondary bedrooms all with ceiling fans and walk in closets.  Kitchen is big with lots of cabinets, counter space and breakfast bar.
Super private backyard with covered patio, built in fire place and beautiful iron fence in the back.  New roof in 2023. New AC unit in September 2023.
Motivated seller!  Bring all offers!  $2000 Seller Concessions.
